        <h2>Implementing Plant Therapy in Your Life</h2>
        <p>Follow these tips to incorporate plants into your daily routine and improve your mental well-being:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Choose low-maintenance house plants that suit your lifestyle.</li>
          <li>Create a dedicated space for your plants to thrive.</li>
          <li>Develop a watering and care routine that suits each plant's needs.</li>
          <li>Explore different plant species to create a diverse indoor ecosystem.</li>
          <li>Engage with your plants through pruning, repotting, and other nurturing activities.</li>
        </ul>
